{"tid":667612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［打不死系列］妻施家暴10年驅車輾夫","createTime":"2018-05-17T01:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T01:58:35.000Z","uid":149515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"33b48d71443d274193ae38419fda5a224ccd7087","tid":667612,"uid":149515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"去年十月，朱男與何女在私家車上發生爭執，朱男下車準備過馬路，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">何女駕車從後方加速，直接將朱男撞飛並輾過。</span>有途人見狀報警，將朱男救出送院治療。醫生診斷指，朱男頭部血腫、右鎖骨骨折、右大腿和小腿粉碎性骨折等，經司法鑑定為輕傷等級。因這次事故，朱男才自爆長年遭妻子家暴的經歷。<br />\n<br />\n約十年前，何女<span style=\"font-size: large;\">曾拿酒樽扑在朱男頭上，致其頭破血流</span>。三年前，何女因吵架<span style=\"font-size: large;\">用水果刀捅進朱男胸部，令他血流如注</span>。另外，何女與朱男吵架後，曾<span style=\"font-size: large;\">走到四樓高的天台扔下砧板，擲中正駕駛電動車的朱男頭部</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">比著我 是但一樣都死左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果然係強國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仍原諒惡妻求輕判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然朱男飽受委屈，但當何女因涉嫌故意傷害罪受審時，他還是原諒了妻子，請求法院輕判。惟朱男無法再忍受妻子的暴力行為，向法院訴請離婚。法庭審理認為，案件因家庭糾紛引發，酌情從輕處罰，一審以故意傷害罪判處何女十個月徒刑，緩刑一年六個月。兩人的婚姻關係終於在本月十一日劃上句號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180515/mobile/odn-20180515-0515_00178_023.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20180515%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20180515-0515_00178_023.html&d=K5WjfG8rMEJ21Oddyi0VqPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a92fba09\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20180515/mobile/odn-20180515-0515_00178_023.html</a>"},{"pid":"b3d7f74723b3a5639ea1d29e79ad227ad99654f9","tid":667612,"uid":48161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:53:21.000Z","msg":"醫生診斷指，朱男頭部血腫、右鎖骨骨折、右大腿和小腿粉碎性骨折等，經司法鑑定為輕傷等級。<br />\n<br />\n咁都係輕傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cc6ec44d205740753315d08eee3b3619c96bca","tid":667612,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7dbf11267c0418f7bd356f492caa54b79c3f94","tid":667612,"uid":149515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名好match<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}